aa(lp216
VIn my own field of investigative journalism, we're also
p217
aVhaving to start thinking globally, so this is a site called
p218
aVInvestigative Dashboard. And if you're trying to track
p219
aVa dictator's assets, for example, Hosni Mubarak,
p220
aVyou know, he's just funneling out cash from his country
p221
aVwhen he knows he's in trouble, and what you want to do
p222
aVto investigate that is, you need to have access to
p223
aVall of the world's, as many as you can,
p224
aVcompanies' house registrations databases.
p225
aVSo this is a website that tries to agglomerate all of those
p226
aVdatabases into one place so you can start searching for,
p227
aVyou know, his relatives, his friends, the head of his security services.
p228
aVYou can try and find out how he's moving out assets
p229
aVfrom that country.
