aa(lp293
VThe other thing is that power is incredibly seductive,
p294
aVand you must have two real qualities, I think,
p295
aVwhen you come to the table, when you're dealing
p296
aVwith power, talking about power,
p297
aVbecause of its seductive capacity.
p298
aVYou've got to have skepticism and humility.
p299
aVSkepticism, because you must always be challenging.
p300
aVI want to see why do you \u2014 you just say so? That's not good enough.
p301
aVI want to see the evidence behind why that's so.
p302
aVAnd humility because we are all human. We all make mistakes.
p303
aVAnd if you don't have skepticism and humility,
p304
aVthen it's a really short journey to go from reformer
p305
aVto autocrat, and I think you only have to read "Animal Farm"
p306
aVto get that message about how power corrupts people.
